Module 3 Tinkercad Link : https://www.tinkercad.com/things/c21vD4Sp4XW-temperaturesensortmp36?sharecode=dSKJyEBqZbmHGICr0EBAV5L0sb82blsVsU-U6I55AN4

Aim : To create a simple temperature sensor and explain the flaws behind standard commercial equipment in Martian frigid environments

Outcome : 
> Learnt how to use DHT11 and TMP36 sensors
> Understood analog pins of Arduino boards on a much fundamental basis
> Figured how to convert analog inputs to voltages and temperatures
> Elaborated on why commerical systems will fail and presented an alternative solution tocombat this issue
